            <description><![CDATA[1rem等于多少px]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_U_oW" id="公式">公式<a class="hash-link" href="#公式" title="标题的直接链接">​</a></h2><p>1rem = html根元素设定的font-size的px值</p><p>假设：</p><div class="language-css codeBlockContainer_EQep theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#F8F8F2;--prism-background-color:#282A36"><div class="codeBlockContent_pSNX"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-css codeBlock_GPoI thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_u3eE"><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token selector" style="color:rgb(255, 121, 198)">html</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:rgb(248, 248, 242)">{</span><span class="token property">font-size</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:rgb(248, 248, 242)">:</span><span class="token number">14</span><span class="token unit">px</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:rgb(248, 248, 242)">}</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup_BUIa"><button type="button" aria-label="复制代码到剪贴板" title="复制" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_hexO" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="copyButtonIcon_csNT" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_B3FD" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div><p>设计稿为宽度42px,高度为35px,换算成rem就是：</p><p>42/14=3rem，35/14=2.5rem。（14就是html的font-size）</p>]]></content:encoded>
            <category>1rem等于多少px</category>
        </item>
